# Dockerfile for DCP AI Scouting Platform Scheduler
#
# This Dockerfile sets up the environment for running the scheduler component
# of the DCP AI Scouting Platform. The scheduler is responsible for automated
# data collection, processing, and maintenance tasks.
#
# It should:
# 1. Use Python 3.9 as the base image
# 2. Install system dependencies (build-essential, libpq-dev for PostgreSQL)
# 3. Install Python dependencies from requirements.txt
# 4. Set up the application code
# 5. Configure environment variables
# 6. Define the command to run the scheduler